    <!--
        Short per-category labels shown in the 2x2 widget's chip row. Plural form so the noun
        agrees with the count ("1 screenshot" vs "3 screenshots"). Kept deliberately short —
        the row joins up to three entries with ` · ` and still has to fit a 2x2 footprint.
    -->
